OL,3,CFamily's call for change after cancer
OL,4,Cdiagnosis sparked financial struggle
OL,6,FA cancer patient from Keynsham is
OL,7,Fcalling for better access to financial
OL,8,Fsupport for critically ill people
OL,9,Fafter having to work full-time and
OL,10,Fhave chemotherapy at the same time.
OL,12,FHarvey Marcus said he and his wife,
OL,13,FJules Chappell, were "floored" after
OL,14,Fhe was diagnosed with leukaemia two
OL,15,Fyears ago.
OL,17,FHe said it forced his family to
OL,18,Fdrastically cut costs and navigate a
OL,19,F"nightmare" and "hidden benefits
OL,20,Fsystem".
