OL,3,CFamily's call for change after cancer
OL,4,Cdiagnosis sparked financial struggle
OL,6,FHarvey said: "It sort of floored us
OL,7,Freally because it was completely out
OL,8,Fof the blue.
OL,10,F"I went straight into chemotherapy so
OL,11,Feverything just happened at 100 miles
OL,12,Fper hour - I was off work for a year.
OL,14,F"I've met so many people that are
OL,15,Fgoing through treatments in
OL,16,Fchemotherapy wards that were having to
OL,17,Fgo back to work like we're having to
OL,18,Fdo the treatment and work at the same
OL,19,Ftime."
