OL,3,CFamily's call for change after cancer
OL,4,Cdiagnosis sparked financial struggle
OL,6,FHarvey went in for an intense period
OL,7,Fof chemotherapy after collapsing at
OL,8,Fhome.
OL,10,FHe later underwent a stem cell
OL,11,Ftransplant, affecting his immune
OL,12,Fsystem and making it impossible for
OL,13,Fhim to work.
OL,15,FJules said: "It was just about the
OL,16,Ftime of the cost of living crisis
OL,17,Freally starting to kick in as well.
OL,19,F"I had to go back to work full-time
OL,20,Fbut I was working part-time because
OL,21,Fwe've got small children.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
