OL,3,CFamily's call for change after cancer
OL,4,Cdiagnosis sparked financial struggle
OL,6,F"One of the hardest moments for me was
OL,7,Fthinking 'can I still afford to pay
OL,8,Ffor the kids' swimming?' which sounds
OL,9,Freally silly.
OL,11,F"I appreciate that it is a big luxury
OL,12,Fbut actually you feel like such an
OL,13,Fawful parent for even having to think
OL,14,Fabout having to stop those activities."
OL,16,FHarvey was put on sick pay by his
OL,17,Femployer which was reduced after six
OL,18,Fmonths - and he is grateful for their
OL,19,Fongoing support but he says their
OL,20,Ffinancial worries put his young family
OL,21,Funder enormous pressure.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
