OL,3,CFamily's call for change after cancer
OL,4,Cdiagnosis sparked financial struggle
OL,6,FThe couple eventually accessed a
OL,7,Fbenefit known as Employment Support
OL,8,FAllowance.
OL,10,FJules said: "It's actually quite a
OL,11,Fhidden benefit so we only found out
OL,12,Fabout it because Harvey had some
OL,13,Fcounselling through Macmillan.
OL,15,F"They suggested that we have a
OL,16,Fbenefits assessment which we hadn't
OL,17,Fthought about because I was still
OL,18,Fworking."
