OL,3,CFamily's call for change after cancer
OL,4,Cdiagnosis sparked financial struggle
OL,6,FThe charity Anthony Nolan, which
OL,7,Fhelped organise Harvey's transplant,
OL,8,Fsays more people with critical
OL,9,Fillnesses are struggling financially.
OL,11,FHead of policy and public affairs at
OL,12,FAnthony Nolan, Yasmin Sheikh, said 63%
OL,13,Fof people the chairity spoke to had
OL,14,Fstruggled to be able to afford
OL,15,Fnutritious food in the past 12 months
OL,16,Fand 27% had struggled to pay their
OL,17,Frent or their mortgage.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
