OL,3,CFamily's call for change after cancer
OL,4,Cdiagnosis sparked financial struggle
OL,6,F"Lots of people call us to tell us
OL,7,Fabout some of the difficulties that
OL,8,Fwe're facing with their finances
OL,9,Fduring their treatment."
OL,11,FA spokesperson for the Department for
OL,12,FWork and Pensions said: "No one should
OL,13,Fsuffer financial hardship because of a
OL,14,Fhealth condition, which is why we are
OL,15,Freforming Statutory Sick Pay as part
OL,16,Fof the Employment Rights Bill to offer
OL,17,Fbetter support and improve health
OL,18,Foutcomes."
